      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "EQUIVOCAL (2) was sent out long odds last time but rocketed out of the boxes with a fast early sectional and gave a sight before being swallowed up late, finishing a 6 length second (31.25) over 531m at Gawler. Can go on with it. SIGNIFICANT (4) doesn't win out of turn. Better run when finding the frame last time though, finishing second (23.68) at Gawler. Leading player again. CANYA FEEL IT (7) turned in a good run last time, finishing in the placings (22.95) at Murray Bridge in a Grade 6. Lines up from box 7 for the first time. Expecting another good run. LOCKERBIE (5) can sneak into the finish while fresh.",
